<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>외국인 근로자 신분증·여권 자가보관 확인 서약서</title>
  <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <!-- SheetJS CDN for Excel processing -->
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* A4 Paper Styling for Screen Display */
    .a4-page {
      width: 210mm;
      min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 16mm 15mm;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 4px;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Print Optimization for Exact A4 Page Fit */
    @media print {
      @page {
        size: A4 portrait;
        margin: 0;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #ffffff !important;
        padding: 0 !important;
      }
      .no-print {
        display: none !important;
      }
      .a4-page {
        width: 100% !important;
        min-height: 100vh !important;
        box-shadow: none !important;
        border-radius: 0 !important;
        padding: 14mm 12mm !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        page-break-after: always;
        page-break-inside: avoid;
      }
      input {
        border: none !important;
        background: transparent !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

  <!-- Upper Controls Bar (Screen Only) -->
  <header class="no-print sticky top-0 z-50 bg-slate-900 text-white shadow-md">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-2.5 flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center gap-2">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
        <span class="bg-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-white tracking-wide uppercase">ESG 실사 표준</span>
        <h1 class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">외국인 근로자 신분증 자가보관 확인서</h1>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Excel Batch Tools & Actions -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs">
        <!-- Excel Download Button -->
        <button onclick="downloadExcelTemplate()" class="bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-600 text-slate-100 font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded flex items-center gap-1.5 border border-emerald-500/50 shadow-sm transition">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
          📥 엑셀 샘플 양식 다운로드
        </button>

        <!-- Excel Upload Button -->
        <label class="bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer transition shadow-sm">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12"></path></svg>
          📤 엑셀 파일 가져오기
          <input type="file" id="excel-file-input" accept=".xlsx, .xls, .csv" class="hidden" onchange="handleExcelUpload(event)">
        </label>

        <!-- Record Selector (Uploaded mode) -->
        <div id="worker-select-container" class="hidden items-center gap-1.5 bg-slate-800 px-2.5 py-1 rounded border border-slate-700">
          <span class="text-amber-300 font-bold">📄 인쇄 대상:</span>
          <select id="worker-dropdown" onchange="handleWorkerSelection(this.value)" class="bg-slate-900 text-emerald-300 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded focus:outline-none border border-slate-700">
          </select>
        </div>

        <!-- Language Selector Dropdown -->
        <div id="lang-select-wrapper" class="flex items-center gap-1">
          <label for="lang-select" class="text-slate-300 font-medium whitespace-nowrap">🌐 언어:</label>
          <select id="lang-select" onchange="setLanguage(this.value)" class="bg-slate-800 text-slate-100 text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded border border-blue-500/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 cursor-pointer shadow-sm">
            <option value="en">English (영어)</option>
            <option value="china">중국 (China - 中文)</option>
            <option value="vietnam" selected>베트남 (Vietnam - Tiếng Việt)</option>
            <option value="thailand">태국 (Thailand - ไทย)</option>
            <option value="mongolia">몽골 (Mongolia - Монгол)</option>
            <option value="philippines">필리핀 (Philippines - Tagalog)</option>
            <option value="indonesia">인도네시아 (Indonesia - Bahasa Indonesia)</option>
            <option value="cambodia">캄보디아 (Cambodia - ភាសាខ្មែរ)</option>
            <option value="uzbek">우즈베키스탄 (Uzbekistan - O'zbek)</option>
            <option value="myanmar">미얀마 (Myanmar - မြန်မာ)</option>
            <option value="bangladesh">방글라데시 (Bangladesh - বাংলা)</option>
            <option value="nepal">네팔 (Nepal - नेपाली)</option>
            <option value="srilanka">스리랑카 (Sri Lanka - සිංහල)</option>
            <option value="kyrgyzstan">키르기스스탄 (Kyrgyzstan - Кыргызча)</option>
            <option value="pakistan">파키스탄 (Pakistan - اردو)</option>
            <option value="laos">라오스 (Laos - ພາສາລາວ)</option>
            <option value="easttimor">동티모르 (East Timor - Tetun)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Print Button -->
        <button onclick="window.print()" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded flex items-center gap-1.5 shadow-sm transition whitespace-nowrap">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 17h2a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h6a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2zm8-12V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4h10z"></path></svg>
          인쇄 / PDF 저장
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- User Instructions Guide (Screen Only / No Print) -->
  <section class="no-print max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 mt-4 mb-2">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden group" open>
      <summary class="bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200/80 px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between transition select-none">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-1 rounded-md text-xs">📖</span>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">사용 방법 및 엑셀 일괄 작성 가이드 (RBA & ILO 실사 대응)</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200">▼</span>
      </summary>
      
      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        <!-- Step Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border border-slate-200 shadow-2xs">
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[11px]">1</span>
              양식 다운로드
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-[11px]">상단 <span class="font-semibold text-emerald-700">📥 엑셀 샘플 양식 다운로드</span> 버튼을 클릭하여 표준 작성 파일(<code class="bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded border border-slate-200 text-slate-800">.xlsx</code>)을 다운로드합니다.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border border-slate-200 shadow-2xs">
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[11px]">2</span>
              엑셀 명단 작성
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-[11px]">근로자 정보 및 언어코드를 작성합니다. 여권/외국인등록번호 뒷자리는 반드시 마스킹(<code class="bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 font-bold px-1 rounded">****</code>) 처리합니다.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border border-slate-200 shadow-2xs">
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[11px]">3</span>
              파일 가져오기
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-[11px]">작성 완료된 엑셀 파일을 <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700">📤 엑셀 파일 가져오기</span> 버튼으로 업로드하여 자동 변환시킵니다.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border border-slate-200 shadow-2xs">
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[11px]">4</span>
              일괄 인쇄 / PDF 저장
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-[11px]">전체 근로자의 서약서가 모국어로 자동 매칭되어 A4 규격으로 생성되며, 한 번에 PDF 저장 및 출력이 가능합니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Detail Table Guide -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded border border-slate-200 p-3">
          <div class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[12px]">
            <span>📋</span> 엑셀 주요 컬럼 작성 규칙 및 언어 코드 안내
          </div>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse text-[11px]">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-slate-100 border-b border-slate-200 text-slate-700">
                  <th class="p-1.5 font-semibold w-1/6">컬럼명</th>
                  <th class="p-1.5 font-semibold w-1/4">작성 예시</th>
                  <th class="p-1.5 font-semibold">설명 및 작성 주의사항</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-1.5 font-medium text-slate-800">회사명</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-600">(주)한국에이비시</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-500">사업장 공식 법인/회사명 입력</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-1.5 font-medium text-slate-800">근로자성명</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-600">NGUYEN VAN A</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-500">여권/외국인등록증상의 영문 성명 작성 (또는 한글 병기)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-1.5 font-medium text-slate-800">신분증/여권번호</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-600">M1234****, 950512-1******</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-rose-600 font-medium">개인정보보호를 위해 뒷자리 4자리는 반드시 마스킹(****) 입력</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-1.5 font-medium text-slate-800">언어코드</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-blue-700 font-semibold">vietnam, china, thailand 등</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-600">
                    엑셀 내 <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-900 px-1 rounded font-bold">드롭다운 목록</span>에서 선택. (엑셀 시트 2번째 '언어코드_참조목록' 시트 참고)<br>
                    <span class="text-[10.5px] text-slate-400">* 지원 언어(17개): vietnam, china, thailand, mongolia, philippines, indonesia, cambodia, uzbek, myanmar, bangladesh, nepal, srilanka, kyrgyzstan, pakistan, laos, easttimor, en</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-1.5 font-medium text-slate-800">확인자</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-600">김철수 팀장</td>
                  <td class="p-1.5 text-slate-500">서약 및 자가보관 상태를 확인한 회사 담당자 성명 및 직급</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </section>

  <!-- Container for Pages -->
  <div id="pages-container">
    <!-- Single A4 Printable Sheet -->
    <main class="a4-page">
      <div>
        <!-- Document Header -->
        <div class="text-center border-b-2 border-slate-800 pb-3 mb-3">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">외국인 근로자 신분증·여권 자가보관 확인 서약서</h1>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider" id="doc-subtitle">Giấy xác nhận & Cam kết tự quản lý giấy tờ tùy thân</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Worker Information Form Table -->
        <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-slate-300 text-xs mb-2">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <th class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-2 text-left font-semibold text-slate-700 w-1/5">회사명 (Company)</th>
              <td class="border border-slate-300 p-1.5" colspan="3">
                <input type="text" id="input-company" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:bg-white font-medium text-slate-800" placeholder="(주) 회사명 입력">
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-2 text-left font-semibold text-slate-700 w-1/5">근로자 성명 (Name)</th>
              <td class="border border-slate-300 p-1.5 w-3/10">
                <input type="text" id="input-worker-name" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:bg-white text-slate-800" placeholder="홍길동 / HONG GILDONG">
              </td>
              <th class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-2 text-left font-semibold text-slate-700 w-1/5">국적 (Nationality)</th>
              <td class="border border-slate-300 p-1.5 w-3/10">
                <input type="text" id="input-nationality" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:bg-white text-slate-800" placeholder="베트남 / Vietnam">
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-2 text-left font-semibold text-slate-700">생년월일 (DOB)</th>
              <td class="border border-slate-300 p-1.5">
                <input type="text" id="input-dob" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:bg-white text-slate-800" placeholder="YYYY-MM-DD">
              </td>
              <th class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-2 text-left font-semibold text-slate-700">신분증/여권번호</th>
              <td class="border border-slate-300 p-1.5">
                <input type="text" id="input-idnum" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:bg-white text-slate-800" placeholder="M1234****">
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- Privacy Masking Notice -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] text-rose-600 font-medium mb-3">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          <span>개인정보 보호 가이드: 여권번호 및 외국인등록번호 작성 시 뒷자리 4자리는 마스킹(****) 처리 바랍니다.</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard Compliance Banner -->
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-2.5 rounded-r mb-3 text-[11px] text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          <div class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-0.5">📌 글로벌 공급망 ESG 실사 표준 준수 (RBA Code 7.0 & ILO C029, C105)</div>
          <div>본 서약서는 국제노동기구(ILO) 강제노동 제휴 협약 및 RBA(책임있는 비즈니스 연합) 행동강령에 따라, 근로자의 신분증 원본 자율 소지 및 무상 개인 잠금 사물함 제공 권리를 보장하기 위해 작성되는 공식 확인서입니다.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Clauses Container -->
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-3">
          
          <!-- Article 1 -->
          <div class="border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 rounded p-2.5">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-800 mb-0.5">제 1 조 (신분증 자율 소지 확인) / Article 1</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-0.5">본인은 여권, 외국인등록증, 취업활동 허가서 등 신분증 원본을 직접 소지하고 관리하고 있음을 확인합니다.</div>
            <div class="text-[11.5px] text-slate-600 leading-snug" id="c1-trans">Tôi xác nhận rằng tôi trực tiếp giữ và quản lý các giấy tờ tùy thân gốc của mình, bao gồm hộ chiếu, thẻ đăng ký người nước ngoài và giấy phép lao động.</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Article 2 -->
          <div class="border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 rounded p-2.5">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-800 mb-0.5">제 2 조 (회사 압류 및 보관 금지) / Article 2</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-0.5">회사는 본인의 신분증 원본을 보관, 압류, 담보로 요구한 적이 없으며, 어떠한 경우에도 임의로 수거하지 않았음을 확인합니다.</div>
            <div class="text-[11.5px] text-slate-600 leading-snug" id="c2-trans">Tôi xác nhận rằng công ty chưa bao giờ yêu cầu, tịch thu, giữ giấy tờ tùy thân gốc của tôi làm tài sản thế chấp hoặc tự ý thu giữ trong bất kỳ trường hợp nào.</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Article 3 -->
          <div class="border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 rounded p-2.5">
